title: Outpost
info: Outpost was composed in August/September 2011 by dEViLOCk on a C64 with an old SID Chip 6581 in SID DUZZ'IT. This MP3 version is directly sampled from a C64 with '84 SID 6581 chipset. Used in the C64 One-File Demo "Waste Of RAM" by Arsenic: [url]http://noname.c64.org/csdb/release/?id=105927[/url]
